29:12.700 --> 29:14.230
And I just started to feel bad
for him.

29:14.230 --> 29:15.500
He was clearly a nice guy.

29:15.500 --> 29:17.170
He was down on his luck.

29:17.170 --> 29:19.730
And I reached in my pocket,
I took my wallet out, I gave him

29:19.730 --> 29:23.570
the only bill that I had,
which was a $100 bill.

29:23.570 --> 29:25.800
Because I felt bad for him.

29:25.800 --> 29:26.470
And he hugged me.

29:26.470 --> 29:27.430
He was so overjoyed.

29:27.430 --> 29:29.800
And I walked away, I thought,
what a nice guy.

29:29.800 --> 29:31.930
I completely misjudged him.

29:31.930 --> 29:33.870
How long was I talking to him?

29:33.870 --> 29:38.630
And I looked down at my watch,
