29:38.630 --> 29:41.200
I don't know how, but this guy
must've somehow managed to pull

29:41.200 --> 29:44.330
my watch off without me even
feeling him do it.

29:44.330 --> 29:47.470
So he took my watch.

29:47.470 --> 29:49.870
Not only--
Not only did he take my watch,

29:49.870 --> 29:52.000
