30:00.270 --> 30:02.330
And I reached in my pocket,
grabbed my wallet, remembered

30:02.330 --> 30:04.370
I had given this guy the only
bill that I had.

30:04.370 --> 30:06.800
The $100 bill because I felt bad
for him.

30:06.800 --> 30:07.530
