were sitting in the front row

34:26.800 --> 34:32.230
of a lecture by the theoretical
physicist Lawrence Krauss.

34:32.230 --> 34:35.000
Suddenly, Krauss looked down
and said, "Teller!

34:35.000 --> 34:36.730
You've been fiddling
with that deck of cards

34:36.730 --> 34:38.870
since I began speaking.

34:38.870 --> 34:42.270
